Package: mlBioNets
Type: Package
Title: R package for the analysis of microbiota data using a multilayer networks approach
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Victor Lázaro, Valeria Hernández-Zendejas, Roberto Álvarez-Martínez
Maintainer: The package maintainer <lav_victor@outlook.com>
Description: mlBioNets uses abundances and taxa data sets to build multilayer networks and analyse certain properties of the communities.
